<A>__{the nun's mule turns out of the farmyard and heads off along the track. a few soldiers are burying some of their dead nearby. the nun watches this and doesn't see what the girl sees on the other side, the mingled bodies of hector and beatrice, all pretence at grooming now gone, engaged in fervent lovemaking. it's probably the first and last that the girl will see. a smile flickers across her face before she turns away forever. ahead of her there might be many a bleak night in her convent when she will remember the image, and that same smile will return to her lips.}
